SSL test files for SMERP

Generate a CA certificate:
openssl req -config openssl.cnf -days 1825 -x509 -newkey rsa:2048 -out CA.cert.pem -keyout CA.key.pem -outform PEM

Generate a certificate request:
openssl req -config openssl.cnf -new -nodes -keyout smerpd.key -out smerpd.req -days 365

Sign a certificate
openssl ca -config openssl.cnf -policy policy_anything -out smerpd.crt -infiles smerpd.req

Delete the unnecessary files: xx.pem, *.old *.req
